data.description: First time home buyers and investors, looking for a prime location home in East Cobb? This one is for you! Welcome home to 3066 Alberta Drive. This 1975 mid century home is a 3 bed, 2 bath property in the quiet neighborhood of Holly Springs located just off of Post Oak Tritt Rd. The unique layout features a vaulted living room ceiling with skylight windows, screened in back patio, drive under 2 car garage, finished 700sq foot basement with a built in bar as well as laundry room, and a massive fenced in back yard. The basement also features a private entrance through the backyard. The home needs some updating and TLC but is priced to sell, so don't miss out! There is no mandatory HOA but there is an optional swim/tennis membership available within the neighborhood. To receive $2,000 in closing costs, secure your loan with Hunter Lee (NMLS: 2029844) at Onward Home Mortgage.
